    "All layers had a rectified linear unit (ReLU) activation function, except the output neuron, which had a Sigmoid activation function.",
    "We used 50 epochs, applying the Adam optimizer with a learning rate of 1e -4, batch size of 32, and binary cross-entropy loss to monitor training performance.",
    "To avoid overfitting, we stopped training when there was no loss improvement for 3 consecutive epochs.",
    "We used 20% of the Train dataset for validation during the training process.",
    "Steps #1 to #3 of Model #3 (Appendix A) were repeated 10 times to capture different narratives for creating an accurate representation of Classes 0 and 1."
